   "source": [
    "\n",
    "\n",
    "import pandas as pd\n",
    "import seaborn as sns\n",
    "import matplotlib.pyplot as plt\n",
    "\n",
    "# Load dataset\n",
    "df = pd.read_csv(\"HR_Analytics.csv\")\n",
    "\n",
    "# Display basic info\n",
    "print(df.info())\n",
    "print(df.describe())\n",
    "\n",
    "# Department-wise attrition\n",
    "sns.countplot(data=df, x='Department', hue='Attrition')\n",
    "plt.title('Attrition by Department')\n",
    "plt.xticks(rotation=45)\n",
    "plt.tight_layout()\n",
    "plt.show()\n",
    "\n",
    "# Salary bands\n",
    "bins = [0, 5000, 10000, 15000, df['MonthlyIncome'].max()]\n",
    "labels = ['<5k', '5k-10k', '10k-15k', '15k+']\n",
    "df['SalaryBand'] = pd.cut(df['MonthlyIncome'], bins=bins, labels=labels)\n",
    "\n",
    "sns.countplot(data=df, x='SalaryBand', hue='Attrition')\n",
    "plt.title('Attrition by Salary Band')\n",
    "plt.tight_layout()\n",
    "plt.show()\n",
    "\n",
    "# Promotion vs Attrition\n",
    "sns.countplot(data=df, x='YearsSinceLastPromotion', hue='Attrition')\n",
    "plt.title('Attrition by Years Since Last Promotion')\n",
    "plt.tight_layout()\n",
    "plt.show()\n"
   ]
